snippet.title: Marvel Avengers skin pack Minecraft Xbox One Edition
snippet.description: The Marvel Avengers skin pack for Minecraft Xbox One Edition that was released on September 4, 2014 (originally released on December 23, 2013 for the Xbox 360).  It looks pretty much the same as the 360 version except it's in 1080p now for the Xbox One.  Note, if you bought it for the 360, it's free on the One.
